WEBVTT

00:09.623 --> 00:13.252
I remember me and him
all the way back to kindergarten.

00:13.327 --> 00:15.261
He was, uh--

00:18.699 --> 00:21.691
I don't know.

00:21.768 --> 00:24.999
He was like a brother
or something.

00:26.073 --> 00:28.974
And we had some good times.

00:30.577 --> 00:35.480
Good times that I'll never
forget and junk like that.

00:37.551 --> 00:41.351
And like now, we all got to
stick to get her and protect each other,

00:41.421 --> 00:46.188
'cause that's what Bruno
would have wanted.

00:46.259 --> 00:50.662
'Cause they say the cult is gonna
come try and get more of us, and...

00:50.731 --> 00:52.926
we can’t let that happen.

00:56.803 --> 00:59.738
So we gotta kick some butt.

01:01.775 --> 01:04.266
We gotta kick some butt,

01:05.579 --> 01:09.345
Like I'm sure Bruno's
doing in heaven right now.

01:09.416 --> 01:12.874
[Sobbing]

01:18.091 --> 01:21.026
[Boy]
I really don’t know what to say.

01:21.094 --> 01:23.995
[Girl]
Here he is. Boom ?

01:28.969 --> 01:30.903
- [Sobs]
- Boom ?

01:32.272 --> 01:35.833
- You okay ?
- Yeah.

01:35.942 --> 01:38.172
That was beautiful.

01:39.513 --> 01:41.447
Yep.

01:43.583 --> 01:48.282
So did you hear who the cult
is supposed to be coming after next ?

01:48.355 --> 01:50.289
A blond virgin.

01:57.764 --> 02:00.927
Come on.
I'll give you guys a ride home.

02:05.839 --> 02:09.900
Your mom is always saying, "Wait until
you're married. Don't give it away."

02:10.009 --> 02:13.343
Yeah, and then some cult member
wants to kidnap you...

02:13.413 --> 02:16.177
and sacrifice you
because you are a virgin.

02:16.249 --> 02:21.585
God. I mean, how do they even know
if you really are a virgin ?

02:21.655 --> 02:24.749
I don't know.
I don't even want to think about it.

02:24.825 --> 02:27.658
You're not a virgin,
are you, Boom ?

02:27.727 --> 02:30.423
Uh, no.

02:32.699 --> 02:36.999
You know, maybe if we weren't virgins,
we wouldn't be so scared.

