- Over here !
- [Man]Hey! He found something.

03:17.477 --> 03:19.672
Oh, God.

03:19.779 --> 03:22.612
- Is he dead ?
- Yeah, looks like he hung himself.

03:29.256 --> 03:34.125
- [Girl] He loves me.
- [Girl] He loves me not.

03:34.194 --> 03:38.392
- He loves me.
- He loves me not.

03:38.465 --> 03:43.528
- He loves me.
- He loves me not.

03:43.603 --> 03:49.098
- He loves me.
- He loves me not.

03:49.175 --> 03:51.200
He loves me.

03:51.311 --> 03:55.215
- Not !
- [ Grunts ]

03:55.216 --> 03:58.216
<font color="#00FF00">X-Files</font> Season 3
Episode 13 - Syzygy

04:44.397 --> 04:47.730
[ Scully] The map says
to turn right at the intersection.

04:47.801 --> 04:50.235
The detective who contacted me
told me to turn left.

04:50.303 --> 04:52.464
- At the intersection ?
- At the stoplight.

04:52.572 --> 04:54.563
This isn't a stoplight.
It's a stop sign.

04:54.674 --> 04:56.642
I'm sure
she meant stop sign.

04:56.743 --> 04:58.677
Turn right.

05:16.896 --> 05:21.356
What more can I say about the loss
of a young man like Jay De Boom...

05:21.434 --> 05:26.770
that the sadness in each
of our own hearts does not
express more poignantly ?

05:26.873 --> 05:29.205
A few people have asked
if they might come up...

05:29.275 --> 05:32.244
and share some of their own
personal remembrances of Jay.

05:32.312 --> 05:38.217
I’d like to invite them
to come forward at this time and
share some of those thoughts.

05:40.186 --> 05:42.848
His friends called him Boom.
Quarterback of the football team.

05:42.922 --> 05:45.482
He was well liked, a leader.
He was looking forward to college...

05:45.558 --> 05:47.526
until he was found hanged
in the woods two days ago.

05:47.594 --> 05:50.461
It's the third death of a high
school boy in as many months.

05:50.530 --> 05:53.863
In your fax you said there were strong
suspicions of a satanic cult at work.

05:53.933 --> 05:57.733
That's the popular opinion around here.
Wildly popular actually.

05:57.804 --> 05:59.203
Based on what evidence ?

05:59.305 --> 06:02.536
Various eyewitness accounts
of satanic rituals being conducted.

06:02.642 --> 06:06.305
I remember me and Boom
back to kindergarten.

06:06.379 --> 06:10.577
He was-- I don't know--
Like a brother or something.

06:10.650 --> 06:14.245
You have physical evidence
of these rituals being conducted ?

06:14.320 --> 06:16.948
No. No, just
the murder victims.

06:17.023 --> 06:21.357
So you have nothing concrete
to connect these things to satanists ?

06:21.428 --> 06:26.661
If you detect a hint of skepticism
or incredulity in Agent Scully's voice,

06:26.733 --> 06:29.463
it's because of the overwhelming
evidence gathered by the F.B.I....

06:29.536 --> 06:32.869
debunking virtually all claims
of ritual abuse by satanic cults.

06:32.972 --> 06:35.372
- Is that true ?
- [ Inhales ]

06:35.442 --> 06:38.070
Don't ask me.

06:38.178 --> 06:42.808
Our research has proven that most of
these accounts are false or imagined.

06:42.882 --> 06:47.751
The trauma or mental illness that is
often linked to satanic cults...

06:47.821 --> 06:51.587
is the result of denial,
hysteria and misplaced blame.

06:51.658 --> 06:54.718
You're going to have a hard time
convincing the locals of that,

06:54.794 --> 06:57.957
especially after hearing the
stories of the two girls that
were there the night Boom died.

06:58.031 --> 06:59.965
- Who interviewed them ?
- I did.

07:00.033 --> 07:03.935
- Together or separate ?
- Together. Why ?

07:04.003 --> 07:07.131
Then you have no way of
determining whether or not
their stories are fabricated.

07:07.240 --> 07:10.698
No, no, these are good kids
we're talking about.

07:10.810 --> 07:14.610
Outstanding students--and
the details they gave-- I doubt
they could have made them up.

07:14.681 --> 07:19.015
Let me guess. They told you about a
wild beast entering in on a Black Mass,

07:19.085 --> 07:22.851
the drinking of blood, the
sacrifice of an infant...

07:22.922 --> 07:25.413
or a blond virgin.

07:25.492 --> 07:30.828
Yeah. That's right.
Excuse me.

07:30.897 --> 07:33.593
[Man]
Let me in there !

07:33.666 --> 07:39.002
- Where is she going ?
- You don't suppose
she's a virgin, do you ?

07:39.105 --> 07:41.733
I doubt she's
even a blond.

07:41.841 --> 07:43.672
[Man]
Would you let me by ?

07:43.743 --> 07:45.210
You can't go in !

07:45.278 --> 07:49.806
How long are we going to stand by
and watch our children die...

07:49.883 --> 07:53.216
while Satan's soldiers
run free in this city ?

07:53.286 --> 07:55.686
- Bob, this is no time--
- No time ? No time ?

07:55.755 --> 07:59.191
Hey ! Hey, hey, Bob !
This is not the place for this.

07:59.259 --> 08:01.193
My wife can't sleep at night !

08:01.261 --> 08:03.695
My kids say they can
feel Satan's presence !

08:03.763 --> 08:07.961
We got to wake up
and take action, people !

08:08.034 --> 08:11.333
We got to cast the devil
out of our community!

08:19.279 --> 08:21.873
[Screaming]

08:25.151 --> 08:27.711
All right, everybody !
Stay calm !

08:34.260 --> 08:37.558
Maybe we’re just
imagining that.

08:47.941 --> 08:50.136
My name is Terri Roberts.

08:50.243 --> 08:53.007
I go to Grover Cleveland
Alexander High School.

08:53.079 --> 08:55.877
I'm a senior with
a 3.98 grade point average.

08:55.949 --> 08:58.417
My name is Margi Kleinjan.

08:58.484 --> 09:01.351
I go to Grover Cleveland
Alexander High School.

09:01.421 --> 09:05.357
I'm a senior with
a 3.75 grade point average.

09:05.425 --> 09:08.622
I'm on the cheerleading yell squad
with my best friend Terri.

09:08.695 --> 09:11.926
I'm on the cheerleading yell squad
with my best friend Margi.

09:11.998 --> 09:14.489
We plan to go to college
together in the fall.

09:14.567 --> 09:19.300
Yeah. Could you tell me again
exactly what happened the night
of Jay De Boom's death ?

09:19.405 --> 09:21.600
Uh, Boom--

09:21.708 --> 09:25.804
jay was giving us a ride home
in his truck...

09:25.912 --> 09:29.040
when all of a sudden
he swerved off the road.

09:29.115 --> 09:31.913
Like he had been possessed
or something.

09:31.985 --> 09:35.853
He made us get out of the car
and walk to a clearing where...

09:35.922 --> 09:40.757
people were wearing black robes
and holding black candles.

09:40.827 --> 09:44.024
I couldn't see their faces
underneath their hoods,

09:44.097 --> 09:46.224
but I knew they were
up to no good.

09:46.299 --> 09:48.290
How did you know
they were up to no good ?

09:48.368 --> 09:51.360
They were all standing
around this altar,

09:51.437 --> 09:54.429
and one of them
had a long knife...

09:54.540 --> 09:59.568
with a snake's head on
the handle with ruby eyes.

09:59.679 --> 10:04.013
I thought we were dead because
we'd heard they were going
to sacrifice a blond virgin.

10:04.083 --> 10:08.543
But instead they just brought
out this little crying baby...

10:08.621 --> 10:10.816
and put it on the altar.

10:10.890 --> 10:14.189
The man with the knife started
saying some kind of prayer.

10:14.260 --> 10:17.491
He was chanting,

10:17.563 --> 10:21.260
and he was saying stuff about how
they were going to sacrifice the baby,

10:21.334 --> 10:25.031
because it hadn't
been christened yet...

10:25.138 --> 10:29.905
and how they were going to bury it in
a mass grave on the outskirts of town...

10:29.976 --> 10:31.878
with all the other babies
that they'd killed.

10:31.878 --> 10:32.776
with all the other babies
that they'd killed.

10:32.879 --> 10:36.645
And-- And--

10:36.716 --> 10:41.210
[ Margi ] The whole group
was chanting and saying things.

10:41.287 --> 10:46.953
The man with the knife
raised the knife up over the baby,

10:47.026 --> 10:51.486
and that's when Terri and I
just ran for our lives.

10:51.564 --> 10:55.591
The two stories are virtually identical.
The one corroborates the other.

10:55.668 --> 10:58.899
I don't suppose there have been
any actual reports of stolen infants...

10:58.972 --> 11:02.169
or of mass graves being uncovered
anywhere in town...

11:02.241 --> 11:06.769
or that you found an altar
or any other evidence of a Black Mass ?

11:06.879 --> 11:09.404
No. No, in fact, we haven't.

11:09.515 --> 11:11.710
The problem is that the details
of these accounts...

11:11.784 --> 11:14.651
could have been taken from
any news paper or magazine.

11:14.721 --> 11:19.852
As horrific as they sound
the stories that these girls
told are common, even cliché.

11:19.926 --> 11:23.054
If you detect a hint of impatience
in Agent Scully's voice,

11:23.129 --> 11:26.030
that's because the F.B.I.'s study
also found that in most cases,

11:26.099 --> 11:28.033
Like the McMartin
preschool trial,

11:28.101 --> 11:32.299
witnesses were prompted in their
statements by rumors or stories
that were being circulated,

11:32.372 --> 11:34.306
and there was nothing
to support them.

11:34.374 --> 11:38.811
-How do you explain the burning coffin ?
-Don't ask me.

11:38.878 --> 11:40.971
[Woman Sighs]

11:50.323 --> 11:54.453
There have been incidents
where the embalming fluid
used to preserve the body...

11:54.527 --> 11:57.621
have caused chemical reactions
and produced heat and burning.

11:57.697 --> 12:00.894
I see nothing here that
would suggest otherwise.

12:00.967 --> 12:02.901
What is that ?

12:02.969 --> 12:06.564
- [Scully] What's what ?
- That pattern on his chest.

12:06.639 --> 12:11.702
Yeah, I see it. It looks like a... goat.
Some kind of horned beast.

12:11.811 --> 12:13.836
- A horned beast ?
- Yeah. Right here...

12:13.946 --> 12:16.073
in a circle.

12:16.182 --> 12:18.742
I think you guys are seeing something
that isn’t there.

12:18.851 --> 12:22.582
No, no, right here. Look.
You see that the horns are right there.

12:22.655 --> 12:25.590
No, I don't see
the horns right there.

12:27.427 --> 12:31.761
I assume you'll call me
if you need me for anything further.

12:31.831 --> 12:34.664
If it’s no bother--
If it’s not too big a deal,

12:34.734 --> 12:37.134
maybe you can get me a few
photographs of that thing...

12:37.203 --> 12:40.001
which bears absolutely
no resemblance to a horned beast.

12:40.073 --> 12:42.007
Sure. Fine. Whatever.

12:51.784 --> 12:53.308
Oh, hi.

12:53.419 --> 12:57.822
Uh, hi. What are you
doing with my cat ?

12:57.890 --> 12:59.824
He was scratching to get in.

12:59.892 --> 13:03.055
I thought with the threat
of satanic animal sacrifices looming,

13:03.129 --> 13:06.189
maybe you should
keep him inside.

13:06.265 --> 13:11.532
I thought the F.B.I.'s research
would have debunked that theory.

13:11.604 --> 13:14.664
First off, I'd like to apologize
for my partner's rude behavior.

13:14.740 --> 13:18.699
She tends to be rather rigid,
but rigid in a wonderful way,

13:18.811 --> 13:20.904
not like she was today.

13:21.013 --> 13:25.541
Personally, I like to try
to keep a more open mind.

13:25.651 --> 13:28.711
So, what are you doing
at my house ?

13:28.788 --> 13:32.815
I was hoping you could help me
solve the mystery of the horny beast.

13:45.304 --> 13:48.137
[Woman]
Let me make sure I heard you right.

13:48.207 --> 13:50.141
You say you see horns.

13:50.209 --> 13:54.737
You don't see a goat here ?
Some kind of beast ?

13:54.847 --> 13:57.611
This is a trick, right ?
To try and entrap me ?

13:57.683 --> 14:00.174
- Nobody's trying to entrap you.
- Yeah, right.

14:00.286 --> 14:03.949
There are a lot of loonies
running around this town that'd
like to think I'm a satanist.

14:04.023 --> 14:06.924
But the truth is,
I'm just a number cruncher,

14:06.993 --> 14:09.018
trying to make
an honest living.

14:09.095 --> 14:11.029
What do you think
is going on ?

14:11.097 --> 14:13.725
I think the whole town's
lost its marbles.

14:13.799 --> 14:17.257
I should have been the first
to see it coming, but it's hard
being a small business owner.

14:17.336 --> 14:20.100
- You should see the paperwork.
- What do you mean, "seen it coming" ?

14:20.173 --> 14:22.539
We're heading into
a rare planetary alignment...

14:22.608 --> 14:25.475
where Mercury, Mars and Uranus
are extreme influences.

14:25.578 --> 14:27.375
On what ?

14:27.480 --> 14:30.381
Office hours
are 9:00 to 5:00.

14:30.449 --> 14:33.441
All major credit cards
accepted.

14:33.553 --> 14:36.522
[Boy Shouts]

14:36.589 --> 14:39.353
All right. Move back.

14:39.425 --> 14:41.393
To your zones.

14:42.929 --> 14:45.124
Clear !

14:45.198 --> 14:47.860
- Shoot that ball !
- [Whistle Blows]

14:47.934 --> 14:50.903
Shoot that ball !
Let's shoot !

14:53.406 --> 14:56.136
- Craig Wilmore.
- Hate him, Roger.

14:56.209 --> 14:58.200
Points though for
improved dermatology, Gene.

14:58.311 --> 15:00.973
- Hey !
- Man !

15:01.080 --> 15:03.878
- [Whistle Blows]
- Come on !

15:03.950 --> 15:08.011
Can it be true that these people
will soon be adults bringing
new life into this world ?

15:08.087 --> 15:10.021
I'm so depressed.

15:13.092 --> 15:15.083
Hi, Scott.

15:15.161 --> 15:17.527
- [Whistle Blows]
- [Man Shouts]

15:19.165 --> 15:22.601
Scott Simmons.

15:22.668 --> 15:25.262
Babe-alicious
in overtime, Gene.

15:25.338 --> 15:28.398
Minus the Brenda appendage.

15:28.474 --> 15:31.500
- Hate her.
- Hate her. Wouldn't want to date her.

15:41.454 --> 15:43.115
- [ Screaming ]
- [Whistle Blows]

15:43.956 --> 15:45.924
Hey. Sorry.

15:48.327 --> 15:51.922
- Hate him !
- Hate him. Wouldn't want to date him.

15:51.998 --> 15:54.523
[Whistle Blows]

15:56.969 --> 15:59.233
- [Whistle Blows]
- I'll get it.

15:59.305 --> 16:01.296
[Boy]
Get the ball! Come on!

16:04.710 --> 16:06.644
[Boy]
Come on! Hurry up !

16:09.148 --> 16:12.982
- Hey !
- [Man] Turn the lights on, will ya ?

16:15.721 --> 16:17.518
[ Screams ]

16:17.590 --> 16:21.253
What's going on ? I can't get out !
Somebody help me quick !

16:21.327 --> 16:23.488
- I can't get out of here !
- Stop it !

16:23.562 --> 16:25.723
- Someone help me!
- Grab on to it !

16:25.798 --> 16:28.096
[Screaming]

16:31.570 --> 16:34.471
[Girl Crying]

16:38.210 --> 16:41.543
[ Chattering ]

16:41.614 --> 16:44.879
- [Scully] What happened?
- Another young man has died.

16:44.950 --> 16:47.316
An electrical surge
caused a power failure,

16:47.386 --> 16:49.320
but somehow activated the motor
that retracts the bleachers.

16:49.388 --> 16:51.322
He got caught inside.

16:51.390 --> 16:53.324
- Detective White, can I see you ?
- Excuse me.

16:59.965 --> 17:02.331
I could hear him
screaming, but--

17:02.401 --> 17:04.493
You weren't in
your motel room.

17:04.603 --> 17:07.037
I went to follow up a lead
with Detective White.

17:07.106 --> 17:09.597
- I see.
- You see what ?

17:09.709 --> 17:12.906
We've been working together
for, what, two years now ?

17:12.978 --> 17:16.539
We have differing opinions,
but I didn't expect you to ditch me.

17:16.615 --> 17:19.846
- I didn't ditch you.
- Fine. Whatever.

17:19.919 --> 17:23.319
[Machinery Whirring]

17:23.388 --> 17:27.519
We got more trouble. A mob has gathered
on the Southside of town.

17:34.100 --> 17:37.126
- Okay.
- [Man]Hey, Bob, we got company.

17:44.043 --> 17:46.409
What's going on here, Bob ?

17:46.479 --> 17:51.348
George Hunsaker's boy got a call
from someone who said they knew
the location of the mass grave.

17:51.417 --> 17:54.011
You're destroying private property.
Stop digging.

17:54.086 --> 17:56.054
Our children are dying !

17:56.122 --> 17:59.717
That does not give you
the right to come out here and
tear up Harvey Molitch's yard.

17:59.792 --> 18:01.953
Maybe Harvey's got
something to hide.

18:02.027 --> 18:04.996
We got two kids who are prepared to say
he took them on a camping trip...

18:05.064 --> 18:08.522
and made them play
naked movie star games !

18:10.803 --> 18:13.033
That man ? Is he
always that hysterical ?

18:13.105 --> 18:15.539
No, Bob's
our high school principal.

18:15.608 --> 18:18.634
I've never heard him say
a bad word about anyone.

18:18.711 --> 18:21.612
This is called rumor panic.

18:21.680 --> 18:25.616
It's when an antecedent event links up
with a popular satanic cult myth,

18:25.684 --> 18:28.084
and it increases
the tension in a community.

18:28.154 --> 18:31.055
A villain or villains are
singled out as the focus...

18:31.123 --> 18:34.149
of the community's confusion and angst
about unexplained events--

18:34.226 --> 18:36.251
Like the death
of the high school boys.

18:36.328 --> 18:41.197
There have been at least
20 incidents since 1 983
from New York to Reno, Nevada.

18:41.300 --> 18:45.828
Not one of them has turned up
a single shred of evidence
to support the wild allegations.

18:45.938 --> 18:49.169
- I found bones !
- She found bones !

18:49.241 --> 18:53.337
- Bones! Right there !
- There are bones over there.

18:53.412 --> 18:56.677
- All right, everybody ! Stay back !
- Stay back, folks.

19:00.019 --> 19:02.954
[Woman]
They're in the bag.

19:06.358 --> 19:08.826
Go ahead.

19:08.894 --> 19:11.328
- No, you go ahead.
- No, no, no. Be my guest.

19:11.397 --> 19:14.958
I know how much you like
snapping on the latex.

19:20.372 --> 19:24.035
They're child's bones !

19:24.109 --> 19:26.634
What is that ?
What is that right there ?

19:26.712 --> 19:28.942
- Is that lettering ?
- " R.W.G."

19:29.014 --> 19:32.814
Dick Godfrey. That bag belongs
to Dr. Godfrey. He's the baby killer !

19:32.885 --> 19:36.480
- [ Crowd Murmuring ]
- Who's Dr. Godfrey ?

19:36.555 --> 19:38.546
He's the town pediatrician.

19:38.624 --> 19:41.024
[ Sighs ]

19:41.093 --> 19:43.823
[Dog Barking]

19:43.896 --> 19:45.796
[Woman]
He's the killer!

19:56.208 --> 19:58.301
Come on out, Godfrey !

19:58.377 --> 20:02.006
[Pounding Continues]

20:02.081 --> 20:05.812
[Man]
Come on out! We know you're in there !

20:05.885 --> 20:09.753
- Godfrey!
- [Pounding Continues]

20:09.822 --> 20:12.052
He's home ! He's in there !

20:12.124 --> 20:17.255
- Come on out, you baby killer !
- [ Shouting ]

20:17.296 --> 20:19.526
[White]
Let me get this straight for the record.

20:19.632 --> 20:22.362
You haven't seen the bag in a year,
and you sold it at a garage sale ?

20:22.468 --> 20:27.235
To a young girl, one of the Roberts
family. They live a few doors down.

20:27.306 --> 20:29.934
Why was it filled with bones
and buried in a field ?

20:30.009 --> 20:31.943
I have no idea.

20:32.011 --> 20:34.275
The people of this town
seem to think you do.

20:34.346 --> 20:39.113
Would you be willing
to take a lie detector test ?

20:39.184 --> 20:42.415
You can go now, Dr. Godfrey. I don't
think we’ll be needing you any further.

20:42.488 --> 20:45.685
- Your story checked out.
- Thank God.

20:45.758 --> 20:49.125
The bones turned out to be
the skeletal remains not of an infant,

20:49.194 --> 20:54.496
but of a beloved 1 4-year-old Lhasa apso,
formerly known as Mr. Tippy.

20:55.701 --> 20:59.262
Mr. Tippy !

20:59.371 --> 21:04.707
This may not be any time
to mention it, but someone
is wearing my favorite perfume.

21:04.777 --> 21:07.268
Can I have a word with you ?

21:15.187 --> 21:17.519
- This has gone on far enough.
- What ?

21:17.590 --> 21:20.218
I am not going to be humiliated
by you, in front of you...

21:20.292 --> 21:22.886
or by having to bring a teenage girl in,
on her birthday of all days,

21:22.962 --> 21:24.896
to identify the bones
of her dead dog, Mr. Tippy.

21:24.964 --> 21:28.297
I see no reason to pursue
this case any further.

21:28.400 --> 21:31.597
Not only that, I find your conduct
and comportment in this investigation...

21:31.704 --> 21:34.104
not just alarming,
but highly objectionable.

21:34.173 --> 21:37.370
- What are you doing ?
- Must be Detective White.

21:38.944 --> 21:43.176
If that’s the reason we're
sticking around, that's your business.

21:43.248 --> 21:46.274
What ? What are you
talking about ?

21:46.352 --> 21:48.286
Detective White.

21:48.354 --> 21:51.255
We came down here because
of three unexplained deaths.

21:51.323 --> 21:53.291
Detective White is just
trying to solve them.

21:53.359 --> 21:55.293
She could use our help.

21:55.361 --> 21:58.125
Well, you two seem to have
a certain simpatico.

21:58.197 --> 22:01.223
I'm going back to Washington
in the morning.

22:08.774 --> 22:13.609
- [Thunder Rumbling]
-~~[Rock, indistinct]

22:19.918 --> 22:23.081
~Lay me down~

22:23.155 --> 22:28.422
~Lay me down~

22:28.494 --> 22:30.485
-~Down~
- [Girl] Whoo, whoo!

22:30.562 --> 22:34.794
~Lay me down
Lay me down~

22:36.168 --> 22:39.695
-~Lay me down~~
- [Girl]Go, girl.

22:39.772 --> 22:42.002
Get down.

22:42.074 --> 22:45.635
- Go, Terri !
- Whoo !

22:45.711 --> 22:47.645
Yeah !

22:48.747 --> 22:50.681
- Ha, ha!
- Whoo!

22:50.749 --> 22:54.412
What are you going
to ask, Brenda ?

22:54.486 --> 22:56.579
Who am I going to marry ?

22:56.655 --> 22:59.783
[Girls Giggling]

22:59.858 --> 23:01.826
- [ Group ] "S" !
- Come on.

23:01.894 --> 23:04.590
What’s next ?

23:04.697 --> 23:07.393
'A "?

23:07.499 --> 23:09.364
"T"?

23:09.435 --> 23:10.732
What ?

23:10.803 --> 23:14.068
'A "? "N"?

23:14.139 --> 23:17.165
- [ Murmuring ]
- Satan ?

23:17.242 --> 23:19.267
Brenda ?

23:23.682 --> 23:27.550
One bloody Mary, two bloody Mary,
three bloody Mary,

23:27.619 --> 23:29.883
- four bloody Mary--
- What are you doing ?

23:34.193 --> 23:38.129
You just close your eyes and count to 1 3
and bloody Mary appears in the mirror.

23:40.232 --> 23:43.998
- Come on in, Brenda.
- No, thank you.

23:46.205 --> 23:48.230
[ Gasping ]

23:48.307 --> 23:50.298
Five bloody Mary,

23:50.375 --> 23:52.969
- six bloody Mary, seven bloody Mary--
- [Door Rattling]

23:53.045 --> 23:55.343
-~~[Rock]
- [Screaming]

23:55.414 --> 23:58.076
- Turn it off. Turn if off.
- What is that ?

23:58.150 --> 24:00.118
[Screaming]

24:40.692 --> 24:44.321
** [ " Keystone Kops" Theme ]

24:58.710 --> 25:00.644
[Static On TV]

25:00.712 --> 25:03.306
~~["Keystone Kops" Theme]

25:03.382 --> 25:05.316
- [ Clicks ]
- [TV Off]

25:07.152 --> 25:09.950
" Detective White
could use our help.

25:12.958 --> 25:16.257
She’s just trying
to solve this case."

25:20.299 --> 25:22.392
Detective White.

25:24.436 --> 25:27.496
[Static On TV]

25:27.573 --> 25:30.098
[Knocking]

25:30.175 --> 25:33.804
~~["Keystone Kops" Theme]

25:40.786 --> 25:43.380
Can I come in ?

25:48.527 --> 25:51.587
What happened ?

25:51.697 --> 25:56.691
[Sniffles]
I found that on my front doorstep.

25:58.837 --> 26:01.704
If they're not satanists,
who are they ?

26:22.761 --> 26:25.628
- What are you doing ?
- Nothing.

26:25.697 --> 26:27.858
You've been drinking.

26:27.966 --> 26:31.402
Yes, I have, which is funny
because I usually--

26:31.503 --> 26:33.801
I normally never--
I don't drink.

26:33.872 --> 26:35.806
Oh.

26:55.594 --> 26:57.858
You know, I don't feel
like going home.

26:59.965 --> 27:02.695
Do you mind if I slept here ?

27:08.440 --> 27:12.740
Actually, I'm sure I could
get you another room.

27:21.186 --> 27:25.384
Maybe we can solve
the mystery of the horny beast.

27:25.457 --> 27:27.721
Maybe we should just
watch some television.

27:27.793 --> 27:33.026
There's a movie on TV. Actually,
it's the same movie on every channel.

27:33.131 --> 27:35.599
Weird. I like weird.

27:35.667 --> 27:37.828
I feel weird.

27:41.573 --> 27:43.837
Mul--

27:43.909 --> 27:47.106
There's been another death.

28:00.726 --> 28:02.660
Was it a murder ?

28:02.728 --> 28:06.357
A high school girl was impaled
by flying glass from a bathroom mirror.

28:06.431 --> 28:08.365
- Let me drive.
- I'm driving.

28:08.433 --> 28:10.560
- It's not what you think.
- I didn't see anything anyway.

28:10.635 --> 28:12.603
- Will you let me drive ?
- I'm driving.

28:12.671 --> 28:17.005
Why do you always have
to drive ? Because you’re
the guy, the big, macho man ?

28:17.109 --> 28:22.172
No, I was just never sure your
little feet could reach the pedals.

28:23.715 --> 28:26.183
Will you go with her, please ?

28:26.251 --> 28:28.310
Thank you.

28:33.692 --> 28:36.752
" Big, macho man."

28:39.431 --> 28:43.697
~~[Rock, indistinct]

28:48.507 --> 28:51.874
[Chattering]

28:59.217 --> 29:01.276
Hey.

29:01.353 --> 29:03.913
Loss of appetite.
That's not a good sign.

29:05.123 --> 29:07.091
I'd like to be alone.

29:08.927 --> 29:11.054
Well, you got your wish.

29:12.597 --> 29:15.259
What happened to you guys ?

29:15.333 --> 29:18.825
- You used to be--
- Look, Scott, we're not dressed
like this for the funeral.

29:18.904 --> 29:23.068
We're here to make you
feel better tonight. Carpe P.M.

29:25.777 --> 29:27.711
[ Scoffs ]

29:32.451 --> 29:34.385
Hate him.

29:37.789 --> 29:39.723
Hate him !

29:52.604 --> 29:54.572
[Door Closes]

29:59.711 --> 30:01.645
[Mulder]
When we were here before--

30:01.713 --> 30:05.342
- I'm just waiting for authorization.
- I'm a federal agent.

30:05.417 --> 30:09.649
Last I heard the federal government
couldn't pay its bills.

30:09.721 --> 30:13.623
- [ Beeps ]
- Okay, you're good for up to 300 bucks.

30:13.692 --> 30:17.423
- How can I help you ?
- You said you knew why people
were behaving so strangely here.

30:17.496 --> 30:21.557
The same reason my dog's been
trying to mate with the barbecue
for the last two months.

30:21.633 --> 30:23.692
You said it was planetary.

30:23.768 --> 30:28.364
Once every 84 years, Mercury,
Mars and Uranus come into conjunction.

30:28.440 --> 30:31.136
Only this year, Uranus
is in the house of Aquarius.

30:31.243 --> 30:33.177
That's a bad thing ?

30:33.245 --> 30:37.079
Bad like an Irwin Allen movie.
Things are going to fall out of the sky.

30:37.149 --> 30:40.175
Disaster lies in wait,
especially here.

30:40.252 --> 30:45.155
- Why here ?
- We're in a geological vortex,
a high intensity meridian--

30:46.525 --> 30:48.288
a cosmic "G" spot--

30:48.360 --> 30:53.024
all culminating on January 12 when
the planets come into perfect alignment,

30:53.098 --> 30:55.828
which would be... today.

30:55.901 --> 30:59.860
- Why is this affecting everyone ?
- Some people more than others.

30:59.938 --> 31:05.103
Relationships are going to suck.
Significant dates can
exaggerate the effects.

31:05.210 --> 31:08.668
- What if today was my birthday ?
- Then I'd say happy birthday.

31:08.780 --> 31:12.682
Unless, of course, you were born
in 1 979, and then I'd call the police.

31:12.751 --> 31:16.187
You’d have
a Jupiter-Uranus opposition...

31:16.254 --> 31:18.882
forming what's
called a grand square...

31:18.957 --> 31:21.790
where all the planets
align into a cross.

31:21.860 --> 31:24.590
All the energy of the cosmos
would be focused on you.

31:42.614 --> 31:45.208
You don't have
to be alone tonight.

31:51.089 --> 31:53.023
What are you doin' ?

31:53.091 --> 31:57.118
The insensitivity to your pain
was too much for me to bear.

31:57.195 --> 32:00.289
- So l--
- What ? So you what ?

32:00.365 --> 32:05.701
So you blew me off so you could
snag some shoulder time with rude boy.

32:05.770 --> 32:10.673
[Rumbling]

32:11.776 --> 32:13.869
Back off, Terri.

32:13.945 --> 32:16.243
Happy birthday, bitch.

32:22.354 --> 32:24.948
Right back at you.

32:32.130 --> 32:33.461
[ Gasps ]

32:42.607 --> 32:46.304
- You’re bleeding.
- So are you.

33:05.597 --> 33:07.963
You killed him.

33:08.033 --> 33:12.129
What do you mean, I killed him ?
You killed him !

33:12.203 --> 33:16.230
- I didn't kill him.
- [Door Closes]

33:16.308 --> 33:18.242
Terri ?

33:27.419 --> 33:29.353
[Squishing Sound]

33:33.958 --> 33:37.485
[ Gasps ]

33:49.541 --> 33:51.805
Oh !

33:51.876 --> 33:53.810
Oh, my God.

33:56.748 --> 33:58.773
[Man]
Come on. Over here.

34:00.919 --> 34:03.183
[ Chattering]

34:03.254 --> 34:05.722
I'll let you
fill in the amount.

34:09.094 --> 34:11.358
[Phone Rings]

34:13.465 --> 34:17.128
- [Phone Beeps]
- Mulder.

34:17.202 --> 34:21.434
[ Girl ] I know who the killer is.
I know who did it all.

34:21.505 --> 34:25.943
- Who is this ?
- Margi Kleinjan.

34:26.010 --> 34:28.501
- Where are you, Margi ?
- [ Sobbing ]

34:28.580 --> 34:30.844
just tell me where you are.

34:30.949 --> 34:33.417
[ Murmuring ]

34:37.255 --> 34:41.918
I don't know what you think
you're doing, but I suggest you
put that gun down, sir,

34:41.993 --> 34:43.984
or I'm going to
have to arrest you.

34:44.062 --> 34:46.553
We're not standing around anymore,
waiting for answers.

34:46.630 --> 34:48.565
We're taking this situation
into our own hands.

34:48.632 --> 34:52.034
You can't go walking down the middle
of the street carrying a loaded weapon.

34:52.103 --> 34:56.164
- It's against the law.
- Not if I'm hunting it's not.
Hunting satanists.

34:56.241 --> 34:58.004
There are no satanists here.

34:58.076 --> 35:01.068
Then who killed those kids ?
And who killed all these birds ?

35:01.146 --> 35:04.343
Somebody help me!

35:05.216 --> 35:08.276
I know who the killer is.

35:10.188 --> 35:12.418
I know who did it all.

35:12.490 --> 35:14.481
All the murders.

35:25.937 --> 35:28.132
[Girl Crying]

35:48.760 --> 35:51.627
Come on, Margi.
Let's get you out of here.

35:51.696 --> 35:54.256
- She killed him.
- Who ?

35:54.332 --> 35:57.768
Terri. She killed
all of them.

35:57.836 --> 36:00.202
She killed all of
the high school boys ?

36:00.271 --> 36:02.831
And Brenda Summerfield.

36:02.907 --> 36:04.875
How did she do it ?

36:04.943 --> 36:07.002
I think she's possessed
or something.

36:07.078 --> 36:11.378
She killed Scott Simmons tonight
with a garage door spring.

36:11.483 --> 36:15.647
I don't know how she does it.
I think-- I think she's--

36:15.720 --> 36:18.052
I think she's evil.

36:18.122 --> 36:20.317
She tricked Boom into
going up on that cliff,

36:20.391 --> 36:23.827
and then she pushed him off
and laughed about it.

36:23.895 --> 36:27.228
just like she did Eric Bauer
the other night in the gym.

36:27.298 --> 36:29.391
When all the lights went out...

36:29.467 --> 36:32.834
and she knew that he was trapped
underneath the bleachers,

36:32.904 --> 36:36.101
she could hear him screaming,
but she wouldn't make it stop.

36:36.174 --> 36:39.541
Why didn’t you stop her, Terri ?
Why didn’t you tell anybody ?

36:39.611 --> 36:44.412
Because-- Because
I was afraid of her.

36:44.516 --> 36:47.576
Because she was my best friend.

36:47.685 --> 36:50.085
Best friends are supposed
to stick together, right ?

36:50.154 --> 36:53.646
- [Sobbing]
- [Phone Rings]

36:53.725 --> 36:55.659
- [Phone Beeps]
- Scully !

36:55.727 --> 36:57.194
Scully, it's me.

37:01.399 --> 37:03.492
Where are you ?

37:03.568 --> 37:07.095
I'm at a crime scene, a new one. I think
I have a solid lead on these deaths.

37:07.171 --> 37:10.663
I'm way ahead of you, Mulder.
I've got a suspect I want to bring in.

37:10.742 --> 37:13.108
- Who's that ?
- Margi Kleinjan.

37:18.016 --> 37:20.382
Hold on a second.

37:21.953 --> 37:24.046
- [ Whispering ] Margi Kleinjan ?
- That's right.

37:24.122 --> 37:25.783
Her friend gave us
a statement.

37:25.857 --> 37:29.486
Actually, I'm way ahead of you.
I'm with Margi.

37:29.561 --> 37:31.995
She gave me a statement
implicating her friend.

37:32.063 --> 37:35.430
- Who ?
- Terri.

37:35.500 --> 37:38.469
Actually, I'm way ahead of you,
because I'm with Terri now.

37:38.536 --> 37:41.994
- You're what ?
- I've got your suspect,
and you've got mine.

37:42.073 --> 37:44.541
Why does that make sense
to me at this point ?

37:44.609 --> 37:47.134
I don't think this has anything
to do with any cult.

37:47.211 --> 37:52.274
I want to get them both in
and get a formal statement and
clear this thing up, okay ?

37:52.383 --> 37:56.581
- Scully ?
- Sure. Fine. Whatever.

38:07.231 --> 38:09.290
[Man]
All right, Steve. This is what we have.

38:09.367 --> 38:11.835
Let me take a look at that.

38:16.608 --> 38:18.542
Wait right here.

38:23.514 --> 38:25.948
Detective White's cat ?

38:31.756 --> 38:35.920
- [Static]
-~~[TV: "Keystone Kops" Theme]

38:38.730 --> 38:42.427
[Rumbling]

38:42.500 --> 38:45.992
[Man]
Steve, what was that ?

38:53.811 --> 38:56.780
It's moving !

39:05.523 --> 39:09.289
- Hey, girlfriend.
- Hey.

39:17.702 --> 39:20.034
Get her out of here.

39:24.308 --> 39:25.969
[ Gasps ]

39:26.044 --> 39:28.535
~~[TV Continues]

39:37.889 --> 39:39.481
[ Groans ]

39:42.694 --> 39:43.922
[ Gasps ]

39:49.333 --> 39:52.461
[ Gasps ]

39:58.509 --> 40:00.443
[TV Off]

40:04.982 --> 40:07.780
[ Gasps ]

40:07.852 --> 40:09.786
[ Screams ]

40:12.023 --> 40:13.957
[ Gasps ]

40:23.534 --> 40:27.334
Out of my way.

40:30.708 --> 40:32.676
[ Rattling ]

40:32.744 --> 40:36.805
- What the hell's going on here ?
- Something cosmic.

40:44.188 --> 40:46.349
Oh !

40:55.133 --> 40:58.034
- They're in there.
- Put that gun down !

40:58.102 --> 41:00.195
- Where is she ?
- Who ?

41:00.271 --> 41:03.331
- The girl, the guilty one.
- They're both in there.

41:03.407 --> 41:06.376
I think we’d like
to see for ourselves.

41:06.444 --> 41:08.503
[Gun Cocks]

41:08.579 --> 41:12.709
I think we’re all tired of
waiting for law enforcement
to bring justice in our city !

41:12.784 --> 41:16.880
- Yeah !
- No ! Open the door.

41:16.954 --> 41:20.151
- You don't want to go in there.
- [ Scoffs ]

41:21.325 --> 41:23.816
Excuse me.

41:23.928 --> 41:26.328
Gladly.

41:31.736 --> 41:34.728
[ Sobbing ]

41:34.806 --> 41:37.832
[Sobbing Continues]

41:40.812 --> 41:44.612
[Mulder's Voice]
We are but visitors on this rock,

41:44.682 --> 41:48.743
hurtling through time and space
at 66,000milesanhour,

41:48.820 --> 41:53.951
tethered to a burning sphere
by an invisible force
in an unfathomable universe.

41:54.025 --> 41:56.220
This most of us
take for granted,

41:56.327 --> 41:58.454
while refusing to believe these forces
have anymore effect on us...

41:58.563 --> 42:03.159
than a butterfly beating its
wings half way around the world.

42:03.234 --> 42:07.170
Or that two girls born on the same date
at the same time and the same place...

42:07.238 --> 42:11.641
might not find themselves
the unfortunate focus
of similar unseen forces,

42:11.709 --> 42:16.612
converging like the planets themselves
into burning pinpoints of cosmic energy,

42:16.681 --> 42:22.142
whose absolute gravity
would threaten to swallow and
consume everything in its path.

42:22.220 --> 42:27.522
Or maybe the answer lies
even further from our grasp.

42:27.625 --> 42:31.686
I think it was Satan.

42:32.797 --> 42:37.200
Yes, sir. Satan it was.

42:37.268 --> 42:39.361
[ Crowd Gasping ]

43:08.332 --> 43:11.233
- You ready ?
- You're the driver.

43:11.302 --> 43:13.463
[Tires Screeching]

43:13.537 --> 43:18.167
Ah, Scully, if I’m not mistaken,
we’re going to be taking a left up here.

43:19.644 --> 43:22.704
There's an intersection up here.
You’re going to want to--

43:22.780 --> 43:25.840
Scully, you're
going to want to--

43:25.917 --> 43:31.014
- You just ran a stop sign
back there, Scully.
- Shut up, Mulder.

43:31.015 --> 43:32.015
Sure. Fine. Whatever.

